lass=\"fn\">μ</span> <span class=\"fn\">𝒢</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">Ω</span> → <span class=\"fn\">E</span></span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hf</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Probability/Martingale/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.Submartingale\">Submartingale</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">𝒢</span> <span class=\"fn\">μ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hτ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Probability/Process/Stopping.html#MeasureTheory.IsStoppingTime\">IsStoppingTime</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝒢</span> <span class=\"fn\">τ</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hπ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Probability/Process/Stopping.html#MeasureTheory.IsStoppingTime\">IsStoppingTime</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝒢</span> <span class=\"fn\">π</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hle</span> : <span class=\"fn\">τ</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <span class=\"fn\">π</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">N</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hbdd</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">ω</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Ω</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">π</span> <span class=\"fn\">ω</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">N</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">∫</a> (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Ω</span>)<a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Probability/Process/Stopping.html#MeasureTheory.stoppedValue\">stoppedValue</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">τ</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">∂</a><span class=\"fn\">μ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">∫</a> (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Ω</span>)<a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Probability/Process/Stopping.html#MeasureTheory.stoppedValue\">stoppedValue</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">π</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/MeasureTheory/Integral/Bochner/Basic.html#MeasureTheory.integral\">∂</a><span class=\"fn\">μ</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a submartingale `f` and bounded stopping times `τ` and `π` such that `τ ≤ π`, the\nexpectation of `stoppedValue f τ` is less than or equal to the expectation of `stoppedValue f π`.\nThis is the forward direction of the optional stopping theorem. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Probability/Martingale/OptionalStopping.html#MeasureTheory.Submartingale.expected_stoppedValue_mono","kind":"theorem","line":41,"name":"MeasureTheory.Submartingale.expected_stoppedValue_mono","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Probability/Martingale/OptionalStopping.lean#L41-L67"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Probability.Notation","Mathlib.Probability.Process.HittingTime","Mathlib.Probability.Martingale.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.Probability.Martingale.OptionalStopping"}